OL,3,C'Incremental change won't cut it':
OL,4,CStarmer to give speech in fight to
OL,5,Ckeep job
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer will say that
OL,8,F"incremental change won't cut it" as
OL,9,Fthe Labour Party picks up the pieces
OL,10,Ffollowing a dire set of election
OL,11,Fresults in Scotland, Wales and across
OL,12,FEnglish councils.
OL,14,FThe result of Thursday's voting has
OL,15,Fled to calls from around 40 Labour MPs
OL,16,Ffor leadership change after suffering
OL,17,Fheavy losses to Reform UK, the Green
OL,18,FParty, the SNP and Plaid Cymru.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@aO]
