CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778508672
OL,3,C'Incremental change won't cut it':
OL,4,CStarmer to give speech in fight to
OL,5,Ckeep job
OL,7,FStarmer is expected to add: "People
OL,8,Fneed hope. We will face up to the big
OL,9,Fchallenges and we will make the big
OL,10,Farguments.
OL,12,F"The Labour case that only Labour
OL,13,Fvalues and Labour policies can ensure
OL,14,Four country not only weathers these
OL,15,Fstorms but emerges stronger and
OL,16,Ffairer."
OL,18,FThe PM will go on to say that Nigel
OL,19,FFarage and the Conservatives are
OL,20,F"defined by breaking our relationship
OL,21,Fwith Europe".
OL,26,@oD@]OUtD@AOUxD@HO]|D@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
