OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778508672
OL,3,C'Incremental change won't cut it':
OL,4,CStarmer to give speech in fight to
OL,5,Ckeep job
OL,7,F"This Labour Government will be
OL,8,Fdefined by rebuilding our relationship
OL,9,Fand by putting Britain at the heart of
OL,10,FEurope," Starmer is expected to say.
OL,11,F"So that we are stronger on the
OL,12,Feconomy, on trade, on defence, you
OL,13,Fname it.
OL,15,F"Because standing shoulder to shoulder
OL,16,Fwith the countries that most share our
OL,17,Finterests, our values and our enemies
OL,18,Fthat is the right choice for Britain,
OL,19,Fthat is the Labour choice."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@HO]sD@AOUwD@AOU{D@[O]
