OL,3,C'Incremental change won't cut it':
OL,4,CStarmer to give speech in fight to
OL,5,Ckeep job
OL,7,FFormer deputy prime minister Angela
OL,8,FRayner said Starmer had to "meet the
OL,9,Fmoment and set out the change our
OL,10,Fcountry needs" as she called for Andy
OL,11,FBurnham's return to Parliament.
OL,13,FBoth Rayner and Greater Manchester
OL,14,FMayor Burnham are seen as potential
OL,15,Fleadership contenders.
OL,17,FRayner, the former deputy Labour
OL,18,Fleader, called for a shift to the left
OL,19,Fin a lengthy statement which set out
OL,20,Fher vision for the party.
OL,26,@pD@\OUrD@NO]
